 City, Higashiyama Ward, Sennyūji Sannai-cho 36 |- | Extra || {{ill|Sennyūji Main Hall|ja|泉涌寺本坊|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sennyūji Main Hall|qq=}} || {{ill|Yang Guifei Kannon|ja|泉涌寺#楊貴妃観音|lt=Yang Guifei Kannon|lt_ja=楊貴妃観音|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Guifei Kannon|qq=}} || Good Matches and the Fulfillment of Various Wishes || Kyoto City, Higashiyama Ward, Sennyūji Sannai-cho 27 |- | Site 6 || {{ill|Hida-in|ja|悲田院 (京都市東山区)|lt=Hida-in|lt_ja=悲田院|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hida-in|qq=}} || {{ill|Bishamonten|ja|毘沙門天|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bishamonten|qq=}} || Abundance of Wealth || Kyoto City, Higashiyama Ward, Sennyūji Sannai-cho 35 |- | Site 7 || {{ill|Hōon-in|ja|法音院 (京都市東山区)|lt=Hoon-in|lt_ja=法音院|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōon-in|qq=}} || {{ill|Jurōjin|lt=Jurōjin|lt=Jurojin|ja|寿老人|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jurojin|qq=}} || Longevity and Health || Kyoto City, Higashiyama Ward, Sennyūji Sannai-cho 30 |}
